<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to Java Spring Boot App Created by Dwi Didit Prasetiyo</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f7;
            color: #333333;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .email-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .header {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px 0;
        }

        .header img {
            max-width: 120px;
        }

        .content h2 {
            color: #333333;
        }

        .content p {
            margin: 10px 0;
            color: #555555;
        }

        .content ul {
            margin: 20px 0;
            padding-left: 20px;
        }

        .content ul li {
            margin: 5px 0;
            color: #666666;
        }

        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 20px 0;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #ffffff;
            background-color: #1a73e8;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #999999;
        }

        .footer a {
            color: #1a73e8;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="email-container">
    <div class="content">
        <h2>Hello, {{username}}!</h2>
        <p>We’re thrilled to have you with us. Thank you for registering at DWIDI. Here are your details:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Username: {{username}}</li>
            <li>Email: {{email}}</li>
            <li>Phone Number: {{phoneNumber}}</li>
        </ul>
        <p>If you have any questions, feel free to reach out to us. We’re here to help!</p>
        <a href="https://your-website.com" class="cta-button">Visit Our Website</a>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
        <p>Best Regards,<br>Didit from DWIDI</p>
        <p>
            <a href="https://your-website.com/unsubscribe">Unsubscribe</a> |
            <a href="https://your-website.com/privacy">Privacy Policy</a>
        </p>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>